NEED TO LOCK PEOPLE IN?

01:54.281 --> 01:55.948
OH, GOD.
NEVER MIND.

01:55.950 --> 01:58.951
WAIT A MINUTE.
PEPPER SPRAY.

01:58.953 --> 02:01.386
